description: This file defines a CMake function named 'map_issubsetof' which checks whether one map-like structure (subset) is a subset of another map-like structure (superset) by iterating over keys and comparing nested maps or list values.

methods.name: map_issubsetof
methods.description: Checks if the 'subset' map is a subset of the 'superset' map by verifying the presence and equivalence of keys and nested structures.
